These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, dog
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bluemaster
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, thai
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
3. the bluemaster-smoker is the owner of the goat##1
4. the thai is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Pet      | goat  | dog   |
| Cigar   | bluemaster     | dannemann   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Nationality     | indian | thai    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
City: san-francisco, nizza
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, doctor
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, begonia
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
2. the analyst is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| City          | san-francisco     | nizza |
| Job   | doctor | analyst  |
| Flower           | begonia         | sunflower     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

