.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, cain
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, rock
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, canadian
1. the canadian is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fan of rock##1
3. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Cigar    | cain     | havana |
| Music-Genre         | rock | ambient    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | canadian    |

