.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, romance
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, librarian
2 different games are played: billiard, snooker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
2. the librarian is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre      | romance     | action |
| Job          | librarian   | designer  |
| Game         | billiard | snooker     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

