.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
City: marseilles, hamburg
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, bike
2 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, traveling
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| City           | marseilles | hamburg |
| Transport   | bus    | bike      |
| Pet           | mouse      | turtle          |
| Hobby         | traveling | woodworking       |

