There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, grey
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, zombie
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Color         | grey        | light-blue |
| Movie-Genre         | time-travel          | zombie     |
| Cigar   | bongani        | blend     |

 